<html lang="en"><head><meta charset="utf-8" /><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" /><title>Services - Adult Family Home</title><style>* { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; } body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; } header { background-color: #2D5016; color: white; padding: 1rem 0; position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100; } .header-content { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; } .logo { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; } nav a { color: white; text-decoration: none; margin-left: 2rem; transition: opacity 0.3s; } nav a:hover { opacity: 0.8; } .container { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px 20px; } h1 { color: #2D5016; margin-bottom: 2rem; text-align: center; } .services { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem; } .service-card { background: white; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid #2D5016; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); transition: transform 0.3s; } .service-card:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); } .service-card h3 { color: #2D5016; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 1.3rem; } .service-card p { color: #666; line-height: 1.8; } footer { background-color: #2D5016; color: white; text-align: center; padding: 2rem; margin-top: 3rem; font-size: 0.9rem; } .footer-contact { margin-bottom: 1rem; } .footer-contact a { color: #fff; text-decoration: none; } .footer-contact { font-size: 1rem; } .footer-contact a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }</style></head><body><header><div class="header-content"><div class="logo">Adult Family Home</div><nav><a href="/">Home</a><a href="/about">About</a><a href="/services">Services</a><a href="/faq">FAQ</a><a href="/news">News</a><a href="/contact">Contact</a><a href="/legal">Legal</a></nav></div></header><div class="container"><h1>Our Services</h1><div class="services"><div class="service-card"><h3>Personal Care Assistance</h3><p>We provide compassionate help with bathing, dressing, grooming, and daily personal needs. Our caregivers treat every resident with respect and dignity.</p></div><div class="service-card"><h3>Medication Management</h3><p>We provide safe, timely medication reminders and administration supervised by trained caregivers. Your health and safety are our priority.</p></div><div class="service-card"><h3>Nutritious Meal Preparation</h3><p>We provide home-cooked, balanced meals tailored to dietary needs and personal preferences. Good nutrition is essential to health and happiness.</p></div><div class="service-card"><h3>24/7 Supervision and Support</h3><p>We provide round-the-clock care, ensuring safety, comfort, and peace of mind for residents and their families. You're never alone.</p></div><div class="service-card"><h3>Social Engagement and Activities</h3><p>We provide meaningful activities and companionship to promote connection, joy, and mental well-being. Life should be engaging and joyful.</p></div></div></div><footer><div class="footer-contact"><a href="tel:425-123-4567" style="color: #fff;">425-123-4567</a> | <a href="mailto:contact@afh.wamj@gmail.com" style="color: #fff;">contact@afh.wamj@gmail.com</a> | 7am–7pm, 7 days a week</div><p>&copy; 2026 Adult Family Home. All rights reserved.</p><div style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;"><a href="/" style="display: inline-block; background-color: #0066cc; color: white; padding: 8px 16px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-top: 1rem;">Back to Home</a></div></footer></body></html>
